@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-content">
        <h1>About Us</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            Welcome to <strong>Flash</strong> — your go-to destination for buying new and used cars with ease and confidence.
        </p>

        <p>
            We are an online platform specialized in showcasing a wide variety of cars, from brand-new models to well-maintained used vehicles.
            Our goal is to simplify the car-buying journey from browsing to getting your keys.
        </p>

        <h3>🚗 What Makes Us Different?</h3>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Wide Range of Cars:</strong> Whether you're looking for a brand-new vehicle or a high-quality used car, we've got options that fit every need and budget.</li>
            <li><strong>Clear and Transparent Information:</strong> Each car listing comes with detailed descriptions and specs so you know exactly what you're getting.</li>
            @* <li><strong>Easy Search and Comparison:</strong> Quickly browse, filter, and compare vehicles to find the perfect match in just a few clicks.</li> *@
            <li><strong>Safe and Reliable Experience:</strong> All listed cars come from verified and trusted sellers, giving you peace of mind with every purchase.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3>🎯 Our Mission</h3>
        <p>
            To make car buying easier, faster, and safer for everyone — whether you're a seasoned buyer or purchasing your first vehicle.
        </p>

        <h3>🌟 Our Vision</h3>
        <p>
            To become the leading online car sales platform in the region, offering a smooth and professional experience that earns our customers' trust.
        </p>

